*Zone.Identifier

# regenerable caches
work/

# regenerable per-episode trace artifact (the .ja.ass deliverable, .vtt sources
# and override files are tracked; this one is just rebuilt by a run).
# NB: .ja.ass.review.json IS tracked -- you review on a different machine than you
# process on, and rebuilding it otherwise needs the video + a transcribe pass.
# See --rebuild-review to regenerate it offline from an existing .ja.ass.
*.ja.ass.debug.tsv

